            "text": "Hunting for the car, which doesn’t exactly blend in with the crowd, West Shore RCMP officers located the unnamed 55-year-old driver. Now that person is under investigation for failing to remain at the scene of a crash and impaired operation of a motor vehicle. Even though the local report doesn’t mention it, we’re pretty sure the C8 was impounded as well.",
