            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Now police are asking the public if they have any cell phone or dashcam footage of the Chevy Corvette driving recklessly on public roads and/or crashing, then fleeing the scene. We really hate there are people who don’t get that this kind of driving isn’t appropriate for public streets, especially busy roadways where plenty of innocent people just trying to go about their life are put at risk needlessly.",
